{
  "stem": "22869.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was then in Nitra, which is a larger city, not far away from Bratislava, from the capital.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "These three places I attended at various times.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But there was pressure, intenseness, felt at all times.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were-- there were-- people were starting to crack around jokes, and tell-- tell-- tell what they call today Nazi jokes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They used to use them more as the-- make the jokes with the-- with the guard, the Hlinka Guard, that we had in Slovakia, which was an equivalent with the Nazi SS guards.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we used to, in order to keep up our spirits, so to say, we developed kind of a joking-- not to be dehumanized, so to say, by all that what's happening in our very little mind.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Don't forget I was-- I was only 14, 15, 16 at that time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And whatever was going on in my mind, what the world meant, we were trying to overcome the adversity by creating some jokes, and some fun, and some laughter, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the time I was-- by the time I was about 17 years old, the-- the talk in town was already that-- that the Slovaks want to gather the young girls, and the young men to send them to Poland.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was-- that's what they said for a couple months, for forced labor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after which, we will come back, and everybody will have, so say, fulfilled his norm.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a lot of talk about it, because nothing in writing until it really started around February-- end of February, beginning of March in 1942, when it became effectuated.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they really started to taking the young girls first-- which-- who they shipped off, of course, to-- to a certain gathering camp, to Zilina.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
